Gerrit Event Stream Listener

Listens on events from Gerrit streaming API

Build image:
./build.sh

Debug app (on developer laptop):
GERRIT_USER=<CDSID> USER=<CDSID> ./debug.sh

Run app in production (gotsvl1416):
- Login to server gotsvl1416.got.volvocars.net
- sudo su - jenkins-icup_android
- cd /cm/services
- repo sync --no-clone-bundle vendor/volvocars
- cd gerrit_event_stream_listener
- ./build.sh
- JENKINS_API_KEY=<Jenkins API KEY> GERRIT_USER=<CDSID> USER=$USER ./run.sh
- tail -100f log/gerrit_evnet_stream_listener.log

Restart example (build & run):
docker kill $(docker ps --filter ancestor=gerrit-event-stream-listener --format "{{.ID}}") && ./build.sh && USER=E9426001 ./run.sh
